N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 11.180 - Applicability

State Regulations

In counties of less than 250,000 population, when not inconsistent with the public health needs of the county as determined by the State Commissioner of Health, a public health director may be employed in lieu of a commissioner of health. Notes
